It is near Lahore?

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:03.400
It's almost around Pakistan.

00:02:03.400 --> 00:02:04.240
Oh, everywhere.

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:05.080
Everywhere, you know.

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:05.900
What?

00:02:05.900 --> 00:02:07.320
Yeah, yeah, brick factory.

00:02:07.320 --> 00:02:09.040
Factories are everywhere.

00:02:09.040 --> 00:02:13.660
And the devastating part is this.

00:02:13.660 --> 00:02:15.460
There is a lot of Christian slave families

00:02:15.460 --> 00:02:16.300
