00:02:16.300 --> 00:02:17.140
Christian slaves.

00:02:17.140 --> 00:02:17.960
Slaves family.

00:02:17.960 --> 00:02:19.680
They're literally slaves for three

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.120
or four generations, actually.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.280
You can say that.

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:23.120
You can say that.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:26.280
Because they cannot get out of the financial debt

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.840
So they must make the bricks?

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:28.680
Yeah.

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:29.960
To pay off the debt to the landlord?

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:32.440
Yeah, actually let me tell you something

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:33.920
about the situation.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.320
Monsoon is very bad over there.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:39.840
Most of the families caught in monsoon.

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:41.760
Because there is no work in monsoon.

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:43.040
There is heavy rains over there.

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:43.880
There is no work.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:46.280
During the monsoon season, there is too much water.

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:47.100
Exactly.

00:02:47.100 --> 00:02:48.320
So nobody can get jobs.

00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:50.280
Yeah, nobody can make the bricks.

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:53.640
So in that period of time, they just caught

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:55.800
because they need to feed their families.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:03:00.160
So they get a loan from the brick factory owners.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:01.000
They borrow the money?

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:03.400
Yeah, they borrow the money just to feed the families.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.080
And they are unable to pay.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:09.120
So that's why that money goes up and they get slaves.

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:11.200
And there is no way to get rid of them.

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:16.200
Until and unless you are not go to pay their money,

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:18.720
their payments.

00:03:18.720 --> 00:03:19.720
What is the solution?

00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:21.740
How can Christians help to set them free?

00:03:21.740 --> 00:03:22.580
Yeah.

00:03:22.580 --> 00:03:26.540
You know, the best way is this, without fighting

00:03:26.540 --> 00:03:31.540
or without making any curl, you need to pay

00:03:31.540 --> 00:03:34.020
and just release them.

00:03:34.020 --> 00:03:37.860
We have to pay lots of debts to lots of families.

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:40.980
More than, if I'm not wrong, more than 200 families

00:03:40.980 --> 00:03:42.380
we have been released.

00:03:42.380 --> 00:03:43.220
And not even--

00:03:43.220 --> 00:03:45.780
You have rescued 200 families out of slavery.

00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:46.660
Exactly.

00:03:46.660 --> 00:03:48.260
And not even pay their debts.

00:03:48.260 --> 00:03:53.260
We are trying just to give them a small amount of money

00:03:53.260 --> 00:03:55.940
so that they could start their own business

00:03:55.940 --> 00:03:57.840
to feed their families.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.440
So, you know, as God is providing us,

00:04:00.440 --> 00:04:02.560
we are trying our best just to release them

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.160
from their slavery.

00:04:04.160 --> 00:04:06.940
You know, my heart cry with a heavy heart,

00:04:06.940 --> 00:04:09.840
I'm just telling to you, letting you know

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:12.240
that whenever you saw their faces,

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:17.420
you will see just disappointment.

00:04:18.420 --> 00:04:21.180
Hopelessness on their faces.

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:24.920
And even they, they not even dream about,

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.780
