Thank you for helping us.

00:14:09.360 --> 00:14:12.040
And Asian Children's Mission, we exist to care,

00:14:12.040 --> 00:14:15.000
protect the vulnerable children in Myanmar.

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:16.880
That comes in many different forms.

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:21.520
So first and foremost, we have a home for orphans

00:14:21.520 --> 00:14:24.840
that is right here in Yangon.

00:14:24.840 --> 00:14:27.280
It's called Hope Children's Home.

00:14:27.280 --> 00:14:30.540
And then we also have preschools.

00:14:30.540 --> 00:14:34.000
We have a school for disabled children.

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:36.280
We also have many preschools as well.

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:39.280
And one of our hope is that we can serve the children

00:14:39.280 --> 00:14:40.760
in many different facets.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:44.840
So the other thing that we do is a nursing school

00:14:44.840 --> 00:14:47.600
because we serve in a lot of remote places.

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:49.680
And health is one of the big things

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:54.400
so that we are having a nursing school program as well.

00:14:54.400 --> 00:14:56.760
In our children's home, our hope and goal

00:14:56.760 --> 00:14:58.600
is that they can be sustainable.

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:01.320
So we also have sustainable farms.

00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:04.920
So we just celebrated a Thanksgiving celebration

00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:05.440
over there.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:08.840
And they were able to utilize one of the pigs.

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:12.120
And we got this picture of a very beautiful big pigs.

00:15:12.120 --> 00:15:15.800
And then the next pictures were good,

00:15:15.800 --> 00:15:18.800
gory pictures of how they have made it into food.

00:15:18.800 --> 00:15:20.000
Oh my gosh.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:23.400
Well, I like a good Texas barbecue just like the next

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:25.080
