But tell me about the children.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:30.280
Why are you working with young people?

00:15:30.280 --> 00:15:32.360
Because they really are the next generation.

00:15:32.360 --> 00:15:34.600
As a mother, I understand that we

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:37.640
have to put God's words in their heart

00:15:37.640 --> 00:15:41.810
so that as they grow up, they can really get to know

00:15:41.810 --> 00:15:42.080
God

00:15:42.080 --> 00:15:44.980
and spread the gospel because they are the next

00:15:44.980 --> 00:15:46.000
generation.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:46.720
OK.

00:15:46.720 --> 00:15:49.080
And you have programs for special needs

00:15:49.080 --> 00:15:50.280
children in Myanmar.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:50.920
Yes.

00:15:50.920 --> 00:15:53.760
That is obviously a new concept.

00:15:53.760 --> 00:15:55.680
And we are very, very grateful that God has

00:15:55.680 --> 00:15:58.320
brought this onto our heart.

00:15:58.320 --> 00:16:02.820
Our founder, Joanna, she has a grandson who has special

00:16:02.820 --> 00:16:03.320
need.

00:16:03.320 --> 00:16:06.280
Also one of the teachers, they have

00:16:06.280 --> 00:16:08.960
