00:16:18.760 --> 00:16:21.960
And through that, really, God has just

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:24.920
worked it to be able to help many, many more children

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:25.080
who

00:16:25.080 --> 00:16:28.480
